{"type":"message","id":"750e3fa6","parentId":"f8933d44","timestamp":"2026-04-06T12:26:20.845Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_LhbEQIE3a0vvjloMKJrzFiTM|fc_03233fb5c08421120169d3a66540e8819a9123f564eae33887","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:** 你\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai\n- **Notes:** 偏好省事，不想在初始化上花太多精力；当前把我定位为负责 IT 运维这块的助手。\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775478380843}}
